{
  "stem": "18486.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 252.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I played it totally innocent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said in-- they said we-- we-- we know of a package.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we know that there are stamps with German signatures from Seyss-Inquart, who was the German leader in Holland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they wanted to have that stamp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, of course, when I said we had it, or confessed, then we would have been taken and shot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I kept denying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But finally, it got known in-- in our village, that the Germans were in our house, with this Jan.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so his wife heard it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And his wife couldn't-- couldn't care for the danger for herself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She wanted to see her husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because she knew she probably would never see him again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she came on the bicycle to our house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did it go again?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They asked her for the package.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then Jan said, I know where it is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is with my brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I knew that wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew where it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we had it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Jan said that because he knew that they would never be able to find his brother, and that was a way to get those Germans out of the house, at least.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I led his wife out to the front door, and I said to her, in 10 minutes on the corner of the lane, be there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I came back and they asked all the time for my husband.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And finally, I said, I think I know where my husband is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he might know where that package is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So if you give me 10 minutes, then I'll go to the neighbors, who have a telephone, and I'll try to find my husband.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
